  <h2>When to Seek Professional Help</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>Brakes feel completely unresponsive or dangerously weak</li>
    <li>Brake lever is stuck or extremely difficult to operate</li>
    <li>Visible damage to rotor, caliper, or cable</li>
    <li>Persistent brake issues after adjustment attempts</li>
  </ul>

